            "title": "地產｜DFS廣東道旗艦店傳結業  大減價清貨掀搶購潮",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\" data-component=\"blocks\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"地產｜DFS廣東道旗艦店傳結業  大減價清貨掀搶購潮\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"502\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/lo/mysterio/api/49b0d0ce980e8683d284f9ba2e12c935cf1463332015d8c1421a6fba516afa28/lightyear_networkapi/resizefill_w960;quality_80;format_webp/https:%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Ffortune_insight_694%2Fdbddec0f78d2a1ab4bc25a6950c04ffb\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">地產｜DFS廣東道旗艦店傳結業  大減價清貨掀搶購潮</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">位於尖沙咀廣東道新太陽廣場的 DFS 旗艦店近日突然大規模減價清貨，現場相片顯示，美妝貨架幾乎被掃空，吸引不少顧客趕到搶購。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">據香港01引述店員表示，DFS 尖沙咀店將於月底（ 31日）結業，美妝區已率先推出特價，太陽眼鏡區亦於昨日（23日） 開始清貨。若全店貨品提早售罄，不排除會提前結業。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">DFS 近年不斷調整其全球零售版圖，並已先後撤出澳洲及紐西蘭等市場。香港方面，尖東門店亦已於去年 8 月底關閉，若廣東道旗艦店最終落閘，DFS 在本港將只餘下銅鑼灣希慎廣場一間美妝概念店。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-3c21b677-9ba3-3162-8a48-9f7f4d285efd-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Subscribe FORTUNE INSIGHT Telegram: <br/><a data-yga='{\"yInteractivityType\":\"0\",\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yLinkText\":\"http://bit.ly/2M63TRO\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:http://bit.ly/2M63TRO;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas;\" href=\"http://bit.ly/2M63TRO\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2M63TRO</a></p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Subscribe FORTUNE INSIGHT YouTube channel:<br/><a data-yga='{\"yInteractivityType\":\"0\",\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yLinkText\":\"http://bit.ly/2FgJTen\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:http://bit.ly/2FgJTen;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas;\" href=\"http://bit.ly/2FgJTen\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2FgJTen</a></p></div>",
